channel.title: It's been four years
channel.description:
I'm asking for a summary on the reason why I have never seen a server with custom textures and new added land/objects/effects on to the actual game map in the past four years?
I have recently come back to private servers, I used to play them four years ago but there really seems to be no longevity in private servers because of my question above.
